data.name: ID_WrongCadenceFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong cadence format. The cadence has to be given as rpm, formatted as decimal value. Supported decimal separators are: , or . Example: 80.4 rpm or 85,3

data.name: ID_WrongCaloriesFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong calories format. The calories have to be formatted as decimal value followed by a unit. Supported decimal separators are: , or . Supported units are: kcal, kjoule. When no unit is given, the value is handled as kcal. The value and the unit can be separated by a space. Examples: 580kcal, 590.3

data.name: ID_WrongClimbedFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong climbed format. The climbed value has to be formatted as decimal value followed by a unit. Supported decimal separators are: , or . Supported units are: km, k, mil, mile, miles, sm, nm, mi, m, meters, meter, yard, yards, yd, foot, feet, ft. When no unit is given, the value is handled as m. The value and the unit can be separated by a space. Examples: 5k, 17 miles, 42.195 km, 10000m, 10,8km, 21

data.name: ID_WrongDateFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong date format. The date must be formated as configured in Windows.

data.name: ID_WrongDateTimeFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong datetime / timestamp format. The datetime / timestamp must be formated as configured in Windows.

data.name: ID_WrongDistanceFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong distance format. The distance has to be formatted as decimal value followed by a unit. Supported decimal separators are: , or . Supported units are: km, k, mil, mile, miles, sm, nm, mi, m, meters, meter, yard, yards, yd, foot, feet, ft. When no unit is given, the value is handled as km. The value and the unit can be separated by a space. Examples: 5k, 17 miles, 42.195 km, 10000m, 10,8km, 21

data.name: ID_WrongDurationFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong duration format. The duration has to be formatted as H:mm:ss.f Examples: 1:50:00 -> one hour and fifty minutes 50:00 -> fifty minutes 42 -> 42 minutes 42:18.11 -> 42 minutes and 18.11 seconds 10.5 -> 10.5 seconds

data.name: ID_WrongElevationFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong elevation format. The elevation has to be formatted as decimal value followed by a unit. Supported decimal separators are: , or . Supported units are: km, k, mil, mile, miles, sm, nm, mi, m, meters, meter, yard, yards, yd, foot, feet, ft. When no unit is given, the value is handled as m. The value and the unit can be separated by a space. Examples: 118m, 0,823km, 217

data.name: ID_WrongFieldCount
data.value: Found line(s) with different field count than defined by header line.

data.name: ID_WrongFieldName
data.value: The header line contains a not supported field name:

data.name: ID_WrongHeartRateFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong heart rate format. The heart rate has to be formatted as decimal value. Supported decimal separators are: , or . Examples: 48 or 50.1

data.name: ID_WrongHrmFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong hrm / heartrate format. The hrm has to be formatted as decimal value. Supported decimal separators are: , or .

data.name: ID_WrongIntensityFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong intensity format. The intensity has to be given as a whole number between 1 and 10.

data.name: ID_WrongLatLongFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong latidute / longitude format. The latitude / longitude has to be formatted as decimal value. Supported decimal separators are: , or .

data.name: ID_WrongMoodFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong mood or sleepquality format. The mood or sleepquality has to be given as a whole number between 1 and 3.

data.name: ID_WrongPowerFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong power format. The power has to be given as W, formatted as decimal value. Supported decimal separators are: , or . Example: 238.4 W or 128,3

data.name: ID_WrongSleepFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong sleep format. The sleep value has to be formatted as H:mm:ss.f Examples: 1:50:00 -> one hour and fifty minutes 50:00 -> fifty minutes 42 -> 42 minutes 42:18.11 -> 42 minutes and 18.11 seconds 10.5 -> 10.5 seconds.

data.name: ID_WrongTimeFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong time format. The time must be formated as configured in Windows.

data.name: ID_WrongWeightFormat
data.value: Found line(s) with wrong weight format. The weight has to be formatted as decimal value followed by a unit. Supported decimal separators are: , or . Supported units are: kg, st, lb. When no unit is given, the value is handled as kg. The value and the unit can be separated by a space. Examples: 58kg, 59.3kg
